"""
CTF Toolkit - Interactive TUI Launcher

A curses-based terminal interface to browse and launch all CTF scripts.
Includes a ranger/yazi-style file browser for tools that need file args.

Install globally:
    chmod +x ctf
    sudo ln -sf $(pwd)/ctf /usr/local/bin/ctf

Usage:
    ./ctf              # Launch interactive TUI
    ./ctf --list       # List all available tools
    ./ctf --run <tool> # Run a tool directly (e.g., ctf --run hash_cracker)
"""

